FS01 (File Server) - IP: 192.168.10.20

Folders:
├── HR
│   ├── [All HR Users: List Only Access]
│   ├── Arun Kumar (User Folder)
│   │   ├── User can delete items inside but not the folder itself
│   └── Common File Sharing Folder
│       ├── HR Group: Access & Write
│       ├── IT Admin: Full control including delete
│       └── Other Departments: Access & Write
├── Accounts
├── Sales
├── Procurement
├── Logistics
├── Warehouse
└── Public

Permissions:
- NTFS and Share permissions set per folder
- AD Groups created for each department (e.g., HR Users, Accounts Users)
- Drives mapped via Group Policy with item-level targeting
